      "text": "Which of the following statements is true regarding an electron microscope? TEM- Transmission Electron Microscopy SEM- Scanning Electron Microscopy",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "Thick sections are to be used to study the internal structures of an organism in a TEM.",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "A fixed magnification of 1,00,000x can be obtained using an SEM.",
          "correct": false
