000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Demonstration of bacterial and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3655d8847516927772026e1e299f2a\">yeast</span> capsules</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Impregnation methods</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Silver</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Demonstration of cells and structures which are very thin and not visible under light microscope.</p>\n<p>Eg- bacterial flagella, spirochetes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Differential stain</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Different colours used</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<ul>\n<li>Gram <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b29a1a16ab1692777199ede1c6e28b\">stain</span> differentiates <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c72cd5f69316927771883c73649d86\">gram-positive</span> and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"08cb2b02c81692777188b83845c84c\">gram-negative</span> bacteria</li>\n<li>Acid-fast <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b29a1a16ab1692777199ede1c6e28b\">stain</span> - differentiates <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"440f2b916316927771808b8ad44a64\">acid-fast</span> and non-acid-fas